Description
-----------

This code automatically segments White Matter Hyperintensities on MR images.
It uses T1 and FLAIR images and performs a pixel classification by using
texture attributes.

code to run: wmhseg_final.py 
inputs: T1 image, FLAIR image and the folder where the output is going to be stored

Example:
>> python wmhseg_final.py data/T1.nii.gz data/FLAIR.nii.gz output

 
